<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=3549&amp;p=26454#p26454"><![CDATA[
On CHRROM boards, the pin CHR /WR is not connected, so writes to CHR ROM have absolutely no effect (they don't even make a bus conflict like writes to PRG ROM).<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=38">Bregalad</a> — Wed Aug 22, 2007 7:37 am</p><hr />
